cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and image processing, specifically in the area of style transfer and texture synthesis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning algorithms, which suggests that it could also fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Additionally, the paper includes psychophysical studies, which could place it under cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). The use of statistical methods and high-dimensional space could also suggest categories such as cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
